text: Ángel Mario Ponce Camacho ( Ángela Maria Ponce Camacho) is a Spanish model and beauty pageant titleholder. She won Miss Spain 2018. Ponce made history on June 29, 2018, when she became the first openly out transgender woman to ever be crowned Miss Spain. She represented Spain at Miss Universe 2018, where she became the first openly out transgender contestant competing for the title. She was born in Pilas, Spain. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:LGBT models Category:Spanish models Category:Transgender women
